Hourly and Daily Snapshots

Simple user scripts to take hourly and daily snapshots. Shamelessly used the
tutorial from Mike Rubel (http://www.mikerubel.org/computers/rsync_snapshots/).


Install

$ git clone https://github.com/rgatti/backup.git
$ cp backup/snapshot_*.sh $HOME/bin


User crontab

0 */4 * * * /home/rgatti/bin/snapshot_hourly.sh
0 6-8,20-22 * * * /home/rgatti/bin/snapshot_daily.sh
